item.title: Do i need to redownload?....plz read
item.dc:creator: @Jordanz_Pk Jordanz Pk
item.description:
@Jordanz_Pk wrote:

Might be just your computer?
Restart your computer or use a different one and see if it works then.

Or mabye if you have got on that server before, mabye you picked up a bad item and it freezed your account, try makeing a new one or try this:

Once you log on, it will be active for at least 1 1/2 seconds.
Type ::empty as fast as you can and press enter.
It will still be frozen, but just restart the client again, and log on, it will work then. (Of course only if you picked up a bad item)
